Welcome to iLib, The Course Book Finder and Reading List Application
====================================================================

o Introduction
o Requirements
o Install
o More info

Introduction
------------
iLib lets you browse MOSAIC library lending data for courses and books
and add books to reading lists which you can share with other iLib users.
You can see it in action at:
http://codebrane.com/ilib
The opening page contains all the instructions you'll ever need, including
a link to the iLib video.

Requirements
------------
Ruby, Apache, Passenger, Rack, Sinatra

Install
-------
Copy ilib to your server.
Rename ilib to ilib-app
ln -s ilib-app/public ilib

More info
---------
http://codebrane.com/blog/?p=979
